            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "SK Hynix股價創歷史新高,受惠AI樂觀情緒及SanDisk納入指數",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Z6N_8w.WrY9eRHYhYnl_zw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED2S0FH_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- SK Hynix (KS:000660)股價週二攀升至歷史新高,受惠於人工智慧需求重燃樂觀情緒,以及記憶體同業SanDisk (NASDAQ:SNDK)相關發展帶來的利多。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次漲勢出現在週一華爾街強勁收盤之後,當時科技股在AI相關成長的持續熱情帶動下領漲,進一步提振投資者對與數據中心需求相關的半導體股的興趣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SK Hynix是AI處理器所用高頻寬記憶體(HBM)晶片的關鍵供應商,跟隨整體板塊走高。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1b3d4cdb-f994-3e8d-bb0f-34890d62678c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司在首爾上市的股價飆升多達9%,至1,128,000韓元——創下歷史新高。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場情緒也受到SanDisk即將納入納斯達克100指數的支撐,此舉通常會帶動被動型基金資金流入。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SK Hynix與SanDisk正聯手推動高頻寬快閃記憶體(HBF)的標準化,這是一種新型記憶體層,旨在補充HBM並提升AI工作負載的可擴展性和效率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次合作旨在彌補AI系統中的效能和容量差距,使兩家公司都能從下一波數據中心和推理驅動的需求中受益。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sk-hynix%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0ai%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%8F%8Asandisk%E7%B4%8D%E5%85%A5%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8-040952299.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 12:33:15",
