            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "近18萬人爆倉！比特幣跳升5%重返 7.4 萬美元， 以太坊飆升8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周二，4月14日，加密貨幣市場大幅回暖，比特幣 (BitStampUSD)強勢跳升近5%，重回7.4萬美元大關。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_9ECTGf2ayUi7OeXB6r9Xg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/0786a97010be54580639b3d645bedaba\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以太坊飆升8%，現報2371.93美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"578\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/odsJjeLGTBitk4FMFisDtA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/2e4051947dfec143ab18c5ad73ed4731\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Coinglass數據顯示，最近24小時加密貨幣市場近18萬人爆倉，爆倉金額達5.32億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"786\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NNGglXXHRyfdM616tWvD.A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/a395b15314d2515f96d87dde5e698ba7\" width=\"757\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，中東局勢出現緩和信號，美伊停火談判取得進展，市場風險偏好顯著回升。與此同時，比特幣大戶Strategy向美國證券交易委員會提交的檔顯示，該公司上周通過出售Stretch永久優先股，募集約10億美元資金用於增持比特幣。據悉，Strategy目前持有比特幣總價值約550億美元，穩居全球企業級比特幣持有者首位。巨頭持續加倉疊加地緣情緒修復，共同點燃了本輪加密市場反彈行情。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>4</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股嚟咗啦！邊啲個股有入選？依家訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>唔好錯過啦</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/319pELyQcUJgjFFyfTHlwg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/c49438951954af385e4417485db04087\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
